document_data.name: House Tlanbourn
document_data.mainbody: '''Tlanbourn''' was an [[elven]] house in [[Myth Drannor]] before the City of Song's fall in the [[Weeping War]] in [[714 DR]].
document_data.History: House Tlanbourn was known for making extremely high-quality musical instruments. Alongside Houses [[Lharithlyn]] and [[Shraiee]], the Tlanbourn family was considered one of the best instrument makes of Myth Drannor.
